  "body": "### Description\r\na teku synced with `--data-storage-mode=archive` from scratch is returning 404 for all slots between 498464 and 498527\r\nteku seems to have restarted when it was syncing some blocks surrounding this interval, i was able to extract this from the logs\r\n\r\n```\r\n2/6/2021, 12:52:33.660 AM | 00:52:33.660 INFO - [37mSync Event *** Current slot: 572662, Head slot: 498528, Connected peers: 59[0m \r\n...\r\n2/6/2021, 12:52:59.529 AM | 00:52:59.527 INFO - Teku version: teku/v20.12.1/linux-x86_64/oracle_openjdk-java-14 \r\n```\r\n\r\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\r\n* Software version: 20.12.1\r\n* Cloud VM, type, size: Azure AKS\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n",
